Subject: [PATCH] Add Pipper cloth-fold configs + FSDP-safe in-training
 action-MAE eval
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- inline_action_eval.py: FSDP-safe lockstep in-training action-MAE@{1,12,25}
  on the live model (all-rank unshard + dummy-pad for collective alignment).
- experiment configs: pipper_fold_colth full2n / full2n_fast / full5n_fast +
  smokes. run_validation=False — native validation_step is video-gen (reads
  data['guidance']/['ai_caption']) and KeyErrors on ALOHA action-policy batches.
- aloha_dataset: shard_by_rank for train AND val; fold_cloth command.
- train.py: rank-sharded val DistributedSampler (num_replicas=1 when sharded).
- checkpoint_db: resolve checkpoints from local COSMOS_LOCAL_MODELS mirror.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
