+# absolute joint state/action, chunk_size=50. Data converted from wam_fold_v3 (LeRobot)
+# to cosmos-policy ALOHA HDF5 by cosmos_policy_pipper_fold_colth/data/lerobot_to_aloha.py.
+# ============================================================================
